<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* <span style="color:#707070">[عُمَير]</span> بنُ بِشرٍ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
